{"tid":772633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲大言不慚暗串毓民「關鍵時刻放棄後生仔」","createTime":"2018-08-09T02:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T18:47:51.000Z","uid":43785,"like":27,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"89d0657b953dc83536dfb2a9ec371006bfcafa45","tid":772633,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:22:49.000Z","msg":"Wan Chin ：關鍵時刻放棄後生仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/08/Yf03ag.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2FYf03ag.png&h=0f3665cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲食左藥未呀，屌你老母，串鳩毓民唔幫後生仔。<br />\n<br />\n佢係咪傻既呢？<br />\n全世界都知佢為黃之鋒梁天琦而喊，係最錫後生仔既政壇老人。<br />\n依家話毓民關鍵時刻放棄陳浩天呢個後生仔？<br />\n食屎啦國師，<br />\n我地撐毓民撐陳浩天。<br />\n我地撐毓民撐陳浩天。<br />\n我地撐毓民撐陳浩天。"},{"pid":"6a1b02962a4ef86ba001aa3d849a0b07e54a7862","tid":772633,"uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/08/2CabX7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F08%2F2CabX7.png&h=5eccc604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母傻雲，一次又一次屈鳩毓民唔幫陳浩天。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2020499b9e37484558bea7e2618c12ceb39a8ecb","tid":772633,"uid":135445,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:25:19.000Z","msg":"佢條傻閪做過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb0ec30b0103a0dd74469da23d059b8157f1fd9","tid":772633,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"rep